arabic.title: طهقان زهقان
text: و انا مالي و مال الدنيا دي
و لا حد شايل لي همومو
ما نا كنت بنام و اصحى براحتي
و انا مالي و مال الرمية دي

english.title: I'm Fed Up, I'm Bored
text: I'm fed up, I'm bored, I'm annoyed
I'm wounded, I'm exhausted, I'm passed out
what made me enter this world (expressin)
she suphocated me and stole my appetite
when I used to treat myself good
I used to live alone happily
I'm fed up, I'm bored, I'm annoyed
I'm wounded, I'm exhausted, I'm passed out
I was in heaven when I was alone
No one would make me worry about his problems
I'm fed up, I'm bored, I'm annoyed
I'm wounded, I'm exhausted, I'm passed out
I used to sleep an wake up whenever I wanted
why did my dreams go so far
my heart became confused an insomniac
an my sweetheart doesn't like my honesty
